creator: Complete RE Solutions Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
VaultRE is technology developed specifically for the real estate industry and the first to be created with a focus on providing a complete solution.

- Customise your Dashboard to get the most out of your day. Track your gross commission, keep your open homes front and centre, manage your calendar and more. All in one place.

- Manage your contacts. Online or offline. Attach notes, property feedback, buy/lease requirements and with a glance view related contextual information.

- Real-time duplicate checking by number or name.

- Call Alerts inform you of incoming calls from people stored in your CRM. Forget synchronising your work and personal contacts!

- Check in and property feedback, all in the one app.

- Document storage and sharing. Access to your files without having to be in the office.

- Easily edit your account information. Edit your signature by writing on the screen.

And much more!


Recommended system requirements:

Android Nougat (API 27) +
4gb RAM +
Snapdragon 8 Series / Exynos 8 Series processor +

Fixed
- Some issues preventing the creation and updating of notes
